FROM CANDIDATES:

Candidates Application Data: We may collect other personal information, such as:
identification data (such as first name, last name, email address);
education information (such as institutions attended, dates of attendance, and degrees conferred);
location data (with accuracy up to the city);
identifiers (such as unique personal identifier, birth date, account name);
inferences (such as conclusions drawn about your preferences, characteristics, psychological trends, predispositions, behavior, attitudes, intelligence, abilities, and aptitudes);
online identifiers (such as Internet Protocol address and social media profiles); and
professional or employment information (such as resume, current and past employers, salary, qualifications, language capabilities, employment dates and employment locations);
hiring status data (mapping Candidates to relevant jobs, and where they are in the process).

